After making many various '2 minute' maps I decided to expand and actually make a map I liked playing :-)
This be it :)
The first in a long line of maps from yours truely.. 
Far from perfect but I liked it as most of it was made up on the spot.
Built for a 12 slot server but has 26 spawn points so can do more :)
